'''''-nya''''' is a pronominal [[Quenya]] suffix, 1st person singular possessive, "my"<ref>{{VT|49}}, pp.16, 38, 48</ref>  (e.g. '''tatanya''' = "my father").<ref>{{UT|Aldarion}}</ref> This ending seems to prefer '''i''' as its connecting vowel where one its needed, cf. '''Anarinya''' "my sun",<ref>{{HM|LR}}, p. 72</ref> so also in '''hildinyar'''.<ref>{{RK|VI5}}, [[Elendil's Oath]]</ref><ref>{{PE|17}}, p.103</ref>

